<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Obsidian on carlos</title><link>https://www.carlos2016.cfd/tags/obsidian/</link><description>Recent content in Obsidian on carlos</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>Example Person</copyright><lastBuildDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 16:10:24 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.carlos2016.cfd/tags/obsidian/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>obsidian 如何恢复误删文件</title><link>https://www.carlos2016.cfd/p/obsidian-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E8%AF%AF%E5%88%A0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</link><pubDate>Mon, 17 Mar 2025 20:44:05 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.carlos2016.cfd/p/obsidian-%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%81%A2%E5%A4%8D%E8%AF%AF%E5%88%A0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.carlos2016.cfd/bg/05.webp" alt="Featured image of post obsidian 如何恢复误删文件" />&lt;h2 id="obsidian内置文件快照需预先启用">Obsidian内置文件快照（需预先启用）
