&lt;/a>
&lt;/p>
&lt;p>在「模板」插件设置中指定模板文件夹（如 Templates）‌。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>
&lt;a data-fancybox="gallery"
href="https://www.carlos2016.cfd/00-assets/Pasted%20image%2020250305212044.webp"
data-webp="/00-assets/Pasted%20image%2020250305212044.webp"
data-original="https://www.carlos2016.cfd/00-assets/Pasted%20image%2020250305212044.png"
